@{fg shine}MagzListMan 1.o@{fg text} is a door for /X and compatibles. To be run from s!x,
you need the /X config icons like confconfig.info and <conf>.info...
A s!x-optimized version will soon be available. 

What it does: It lets you select files from AquaScan and @{fg shine}delete@{fg text}
them/@{fg shine}move@{fg text} them to other confs. Very usefull to @{fg shine}remove@{fg text} old files or
@{fg shine}move@{fg text} files to let's say you /X tools conf. @{fg shine}MagzListMan@{fg text} will automaticly
edit your dir<x> files and put "deleted" in them, or if you wish remove
the files from the dirs completely. @{"Install" link installation} it and check it out! 

                           UNREGISTERED VERSION!

           TO RECEIVE A REGISTERED VERSION WITH YOUR BOARD NAME
                ON, JUST D!AL @{fg shine}GENETIC WASTE@{fg text} - +47-33o45192
                 AND UPLOAD A SMALL FILE AND ASK FOR ONE.


                            -magz of megastyle-

@endnode






