@{fg shine}To install...@{fg text}

   To install it for use from AquaScan (what it was made for), copy the
   files in commands/ and doors/ to BBS:. Then edit your AquaScan.info 
                    file (located in DOORS:Aquascan/) 
       (or AquaScan.config if you use the text-config for AquaScan)

                                LIKE THIS:

where <num> is the number you choose for the command (can be whatever you want)


PPC_CMD.<num>=DEL
(DEL is the command used to execute MGZLISTMAN)

PC_KEY.<num>=D
(Where D is the hotkey in Aquascan used to execute MGZLISTMAN. 
(if you already are using D, use another key)

PPC_ACS.<num>=255
(access level to run MGZLISTMAN .. should be 255 so other people can't
fuck your filelists!)

PPC_DSC.<num>=MagzListManager
(The name of the command that will appear in the Aquascan Help)..

PPC_CNF.<num>=YES
(If command can be executed in CS mode in other confs. MUST be
yes due to a bug in /X)

PPC_NUM.<num>=YES
(If you can select files for delfiles by numbers. SHOULD ABSOLUTELY
be YES!!!)



... Well, that should be it actually :) 



@{"how do I use it then?!" link how 2 use}

